e.com/news/music/billie-eilish-lady-gaga-green-day-stevie-nicks-and-more-to-perform-at-la-wildfires-benefit-concert-3829759">洛杉矶野火慈善音乐会的表演者之一，</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Billie-Eilish">Billie Ei</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Billie-Eilish">lish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Stevie-Nicks">Stevie Nicks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Green-Day">Green Day</a>等明星一起表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-announces-new-album-mayhem-3832317">Lady Gaga 宣布新专辑《Mayhem》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
